<b>Subject:</b> YES! That is much better...<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2152" TARGET=_self>What if you could only loot from inventory? -OPINIONS</A> (TheBlack)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>> What if you were unable to loot any item worn or carried, but

<BR>&gt; you could loot from inventory, including looting items out of
<BR>&gt; containers within one's inventory? Would this be a more
<BR>&gt; "fair" system of looting?
<P>Just cash on hand, and one item from inventory (even if it IS in a bag).
<P>That would help warriors and other good Armor/weapon using classes...
<P>--Erik the Red,
<BR>Barb Warrior
